1 A BILL for an Act to provide an appropriation to the department of health and human services
2 for accreditation grants for community providers.
3 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATIVE ASSEMBLY OF NORTH DAKOTA:
4 SECTION 1. APPROPRIATION - DEPARTMENT OF HEALTH AND HUMAN SERVICES -
5 PROVIDER ACCREDITATION. There is appropriated out of any moneys in the general fund in
6 the state treasury, not otherwise appropriated, the sum of $240,000, or so much of the sum as
7 may be necessary, to the department of health and human services for the purpose of providing
8 grants to reimburse community providers for costs of obtaining and maintaining accreditation
9 standards required by the department, for the biennium beginning July 1, 2025, and ending
10 June 30, 2027.
